author: Taegan Goddard
title: Biden Talks with Top Labor Leader
text:
Biden Talks with Top Labor Leader October 17, 2015 By Taegan Goddard 0 Comments 
Harold Schaitberger, the president of the powerful International Association of Fire Fighters, spoke Friday morning with Vice President Joe Biden, “who strongly indicated in the phone conversation that he is planning to run for president,” CNN reports. 
Biden talked “about campaign strategy” and indicated “a final decision on whether he would run for president is imminent.” Related Posts Never miss a Political Wire post Your email address: * Please enter all required fields Correct invalid entries
